Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面我们开始执行搜索并生擒鼬的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓的目的是收集尾兽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三尾很有可能已经落入他们的手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据自来也大人的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们盯上了鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时已经进入了火之国也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是鼬出身于木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前为抓鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经潜入了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也可以认为他会因此而瞄准木叶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为了抓到宇智波鼬 佐助也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找到佐助的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说明一下搜索步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之以这里为中心点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索周边半径五公里内的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有收获 则返回中心点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后从新的中心点搜索半径五公里内的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样反复进行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五公里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么远的话 无线电不就无法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且独自走那么远的话太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索队伍原则上至少两人一组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到敌人的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么着急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的声音皆比无线电传得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子也能及早察觉危险 并加以援助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来说明一下搜索队的编成方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为确保安全 此次每人带两只忍犬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两只 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以跟它们好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是喜欢挑罗嗦的雌性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟着志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子味臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗味臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能和睦相处就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能跟狗交上朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人是人柱力 而且又被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到可能会遭受袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟大和及感知系的雏田一起行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有大嗓门的布鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请多指教 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 作为训犬师的我和牙各带一只
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就准备完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先追踪鼬和佐助这两人的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论发现哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待掌握他们的方位后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先回中心点来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是鸣人 别太过冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波鼬吗 能顺利找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和佐助两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经没问题了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要去哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助还是九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 选哪一边好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…迪达拉前辈 等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找小喽罗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是晓的…叫啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角…角田…角斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那个角都手下的帐房先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请饶我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就全招了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就问问你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤丸 可别输给其它忍犬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要在别人之前发现鼬和佐助的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么慢慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子们不喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了哦 斑点 小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斑点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便给我们起外号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆出这么一副母老虎的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都会被你给吓跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄性你越是追他跑得越快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个穷追不舍的雌性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻若不行就试试守吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和佐助才不是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你这张嘴啊 还是那么没口德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想把我和大家想说的话告诉佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他 大家都在等他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守也不行的话就让我闻闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是隐约能够闻到宇智波佐助的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气味不太明显
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过正在渐渐靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄得我们在发现他之前就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心谨慎些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道附近没发现佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气味远离了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这车水马龙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也未察觉到异样的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是回佐助身边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正那两人应该还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 阿飞 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪一边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾还是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是捡了个大便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该我们俩上了 阿飞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都问你是哪一边了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 雏田 感觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出来 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药师兜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会亲自送上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有胆量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想跟鸣人谈谈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不会再让你逃走了 一定要抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜 你肯定知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子 满嘴佐助佐助的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助干掉了大蛇丸 当真有此事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我给鸣人带了件礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身装束 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然跟鼬长得很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是以前我们组织所收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于晓的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把这东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白送给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在没有大蛇丸当靠山的现今
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用这个和木叶做交易吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 用这东西来做交易也太没诚意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是跟木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么到底为何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和大蛇丸不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并未被晓追杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了感谢鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是份礼物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且你被晓给盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人死后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又变得无法定位自己的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道父母是谁 也不知道所属国家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于自小被敌人捡走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并以间谍身份来往各国各村的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家和村子只是些暧昧的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我成为大蛇丸大人的部下后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…再一次消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有身份的这种痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你应该能够理解吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所说的我怎么会理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己是漩涡鸣人呢 还是九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经遭受过他人冷漠的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会怀疑自己到底是什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认定自己是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强地承受了他人视你为九尾的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人到底想对鸣人干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道他葫芦里卖的是什么药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才会清楚地明白自己的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也结交了认可你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我从未想过要超越大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一味地追随着他的那份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我 真的非常理解你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你让我有所觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也想像你那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要超越融入我体内的大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到全新且强大的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到全新的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你给我的启发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要感谢你啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人是再生的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会成为我必须要超越的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我体内继续存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说融合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是将被佐助打倒的大蛇丸大人遗体上的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移植到这副身体上来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这真是非常惊人的生命力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体反而被渐渐侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的三成已经被侵蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不被吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拼命地抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到一个想要超越大蛇丸大人的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说的只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是在木叶的监狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 抓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待我能完全控制大蛇丸大人的力量后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会认真跟你过招的 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你还要等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是打倒大蛇丸大人的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想对佐助干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会有期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 打倒佐助了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来略微有些本事呢 这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到大蛇丸居然会被这种小鬼干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是现在 我也无法相信 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被一双不错的眼睛给盯上了 阿飞 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干劲十足嘛 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后必须得向鼬道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是晓成员吧 宇智波鼬在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？老实交代就放过你们 怎么办 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可真够强势的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写轮眼啊 这家伙果然是鼬的弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能干掉大蛇丸也多亏了你宇智波一族的血统吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这沾了血统光的愚蠢之徒 你不想说就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会凭实力让你招供的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集是激突
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人每个月的还款期又到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豚豚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就干一场好久没做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在这种地方睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.92,0:22:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我想借些钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 这可是件高档品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖掉的话 大概值一百万两呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 大姐 五十万两怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 那只猪不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 今天是何等地倒霉啊
